<% include ./include/head %>
<% include ./include/musicnotation %>
<body>
  <% include ./include/nav %>
  <main class="light-blue lighten-4">
    <div class="section white z-depth-2">
      <div class="container flow-text">
        <h2 class="header">Time Signatures</h2>
        <p>Understanding what time signatures mean</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row container flow-text">

      <div class="col offset-s2">

        <div class="col s12">
          <div class="col s10">
            <h3>Time Signatures</h3>
            <p>Time signatures are made up of two parts: </p>
            <ul class="bullet">
              <li>The number on top shows how many notes there are per bar</li>
              <li>The number on the bottom shows which type of note is being used</li>
            </ul>
            <p>In the example below, the top number shows there are 2 notes to a bar. The bottom number shows that crotchets (quarter notes) will be used</p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=10 font-size=12
                stave time = 2/4
                clef = treble
                notes :4 E-E/4
                text :4, 1, 2
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section white z-depth-2">
      <div class="container flow-text">
        <h2 class="header">Simple Time Signatures</h2>
        <p>Understanding simple time signatures (Click each heading for a description)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12">
      <ul class="tabs tabs-fixed-width z-depth-1">
        <li class="tab"><a class="active" href="#24">2/4</a></li>
        <li class="tab"><a href="#34">3/4</a></li>
        <li class="tab"><a href="#44">4/4</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="row container flow-text">

      <div class="col offset-s2">

        <div id="24" class="col s12">
          <h3>2/4 Time Signature</h3>
          <p>A 2/4 time signature has 2 crotchet beats to a bar.</p>
          <div class="stave">
            <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
              options space=10 font-size=12
              stave time = 2/4
              clef = treble
              notes :4 E-E/4
              text :4, 1, 2
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="34" class="col s12">
          <h3>3/4 Time Signature</h3>
          <p>A 3/4 time signature has 3 crotchet beats to a bar.</p>
          <div class="stave">
            <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
              options space=10 font-size=12
              stave time = 3/4
              clef = treble
              notes :4 E-E-E/4
              text :4, 1, 2, 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="44" class="col s8">
          <h3>4/4 Time Signature: Common Time</h3>
          <p>A 4/4 time signature (also known as common time) has 4 crotchet beats to a bar.</p>
          <div class="stave">
            <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
              options space=10 font-size=12
              stave time = 4/4
              clef = treble
              notes :4 E-E-E-E/4
              text :4, 1, 2, 3, 4
            </div>
          </div>

          <p>Sometimes 4/4 time signatures can be represented by a capital C, meaning common time.</p>
          <div class="stave">
            <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
              options space=10 font-size=12
              stave time = C
              clef = treble
              notes :4 E-E-E-E/4
              text :4, 1, 2, 3, 4
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>

  </main>
  <% include ./include/scripts %>
  <% include ./include/footer %>
